<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Reset Your Password - MockMate</title>
    <style>
        /* Reset styles */
        * { margin: 0; padding: 0; box-sizing: border-box; }

        /* Terminal theme styles */
        body {
            font-family: 'Courier New', 'Monaco', 'Lucida Console', monospace;
            background-color: #0a0a0a; color: #00ff41; line-height: 1.6; margin: 0; padding: 0;
            -webkit-text-size-adjust: 100%; -ms-text-size-adjust: 100%;
        }

        .email-container {
            max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto; background-color: #111111;
            border: 2px solid #00ff41; border-radius: 8px; box-shadow: 0 0 20px rgba(0, 255, 65, 0.3);
        }

        .terminal-header {
            background-color: #1a1a1a; padding: 10px 15px; border-bottom: 1px solid #00ff41;
            display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 8px;
        }

        .terminal-buttons { display: flex; gap: 6px; }
        .terminal-button { width: 12px; height: 12px; border-radius: 50%; }
        .btn-close { background-color: #ff5f56; } .btn-minimize { background-color: #ffbd2e; } .btn-maximize { background-color: #27ca3f; }
        .terminal-title { color: #00ff41; font-size: 14px; margin-left: 10px; }

        .terminal-content { padding: 30px; background-color: #0a0a0a; }
        .terminal-prompt { color: #00ff41; font-weight: bold; margin-bottom: 15px; font-size: 16px; }
        .terminal-prompt::before { content: "$ "; color: #00ff41; }

        h1, h2, h3 { color: #00ff41; margin-bottom: 15px; font-family: 'Courier New', monospace; }
        h1 { font-size: 24px; text-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(0, 255, 65, 0.5); }
        h2 { font-size: 20px; color: #33ff66; }
        h3 { font-size: 18px; color: #66ff99; }
        p { margin-bottom: 15px; color: #cccccc; font-size: 14px; }

        .highlight-text {
            color: #00ff41; font-weight: bold; background-color: rgba(0, 255, 65, 0.1);
            padding: 2px 4px; border-radius: 3px;
        }

        .terminal-button-link {
            display: inline-block; background-color: transparent; color: #00ff41;
            border: 2px solid #00ff41; padding: 12px 24px; text-decoration: none;
            font-family: 'Courier New', monospace; font-size: 14px; font-weight: bold;
            border-radius: 4px; margin: 15px 0; transition: all 0.3s ease;
            text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 1px;
        }

        .terminal-button-link:hover {
            background-color: #00ff41; color: #0a0a0a; box-shadow: 0 0 15px rgba(0, 255, 65, 0.7);
        }

        .code-block {
            background-color: #1a1a1a; border: 1px solid #333; border-left: 4px solid #00ff41;
            padding: 15px; margin: 15px 0; font-family: 'Courier New', monospace;
            font-size: 13px; color: #cccccc; border-radius: 4px; overflow-x: auto;
        }

        .terminal-warning {
            background-color: rgba(255, 165, 0, 0.1); border: 1px solid #ffa500;
            color: #ffa500; padding: 15px; margin: 20px 0; border-radius: 4px;
        }

        .terminal-footer {
            background-color: #1a1a1a; padding: 20px 30px; border-top: 1px solid #333;
            text-align: center; font-size: 12px; color: #666;
        }

        .terminal-footer a { color: #00ff41; text-decoration: none; }
        .terminal-footer a:hover { text-decoration: underline; }

        .status-indicator { display: inline-block; width: 8px; height: 8px; border-radius: 50%; margin-right: 8px; }
        .status-warning { background-color: #ffa500; }

        @media only screen and (max-width: 600px) {
            .email-container { margin: 10px; border-radius: 4px; }
            .terminal-content { padding: 20px; }
            .terminal-header { padding: 8px 12px; }
            h1 { font-size: 20px; } h2 { font-size: 18px; } h3 { font-size: 16px; }
            .terminal-button-link { padding: 10px 20px; font-size: 12px; }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="email-container">
        <div class="terminal-header">
            <div class="terminal-buttons">
                <div class="terminal-button btn-close"></div>
                <div class="terminal-button btn-minimize"></div>
                <div class="terminal-button btn-maximize"></div>
            </div>
            <div class="terminal-title">MockMate Terminal - Password Reset Request</div>
        </div>

        <div class="terminal-content">
            <div class="terminal-prompt">mockmate@system:~$</div>
            
            <h1>üîê Password Reset Request</h1>
            
            <p>Hello <span class="highlight-text">{{userName}}</span>,</p>
            
            <p>We received a request to reset the password for your MockMate account. If you made this request, click the button below to reset your password.</p>

            <div class="code-block">
# Password reset command initiated
curl -X POST "{{resetUrl}}"
# Secure token generated and ready for use
            </div>

            <center>
                <a href="{{resetUrl}}" class="terminal-button-link">
                    RESET PASSWORD
                </a>
            </center>

            <div class="terminal-warning">
                <h3>‚ö†Ô∏è Security Notice:</h3>
                <p>This reset link will expire in <strong>1 hour</strong> for security reasons.</p>
                <p>If you didn't request this password reset, please ignore this email and consider changing your password if you suspect unauthorized access.</p>
            </div>

            <p>For your security:</p>
            <ul style="color: #cccccc; margin-left: 20px; margin-bottom: 15px;">
                <li>Use a strong, unique password</li>
                <li>Don't share your password with anyone</li>
                <li>Enable two-factor authentication when available</li>
            </ul>

            <p>If you're having trouble clicking the button, copy and paste the following URL into your browser:</p>
            <div class="code-block">{{resetUrl}}</div>

            <p><strong>The MockMate Security Team</strong></p>
        </div>

        <div class="terminal-footer">
            <p>
                <span class="status-indicator status-warning"></span>
                System Status: Security Alert | 
                <a href="{{baseUrl}}">MockMate Dashboard</a> | 
                <a href="{{baseUrl}}/support">Support</a>
            </p>
            <p style="margin-top: 10px; font-size: 11px;">
                ¬© {{currentYear}} MockMate. All rights reserved.<br>
                This email was sent from an automated system. Please do not reply to this email.
            </p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
